{"tid":188530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"18歲嫩台妹低胸墜溝 ~潘漾綺~ D奶濕身畫面美到被稱為「水溝妹」","createTime":"2017-04-05T17:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-05T17:48:57.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56b180c322732134e0ff7596e62b7f1f11457da3","tid":188530,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:29:36.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》報導，昨凌晨3時許，高市驚傳有女子跳入自由、同盟路口的大排溝渠尋短。消防隊趕抵發現一名長髮且身穿低胸花洋裝的潘姓女子（18歲），全身濕透、表情呆滯站在水淹及胸的排水溝內。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.buzzhand.net/uploads/df/f/889335/14479028241202.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.buzzhand.net%2Fuploads%2Fdf%2Ff%2F889335%2F14479028241202.jpg&h=b7dc58d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.buzzhand.net/uploads/df/f/889335/1447902828859.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.buzzhand.net%2Fuploads%2Fdf%2Ff%2F889335%2F1447902828859.jpg&h=03f0cd87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消防人員架設雙節梯至約2樓高的排水溝內，確認潘女意識清楚可活動，讓她自行爬上堤防後送醫檢查。警調查，潘女有喝酒，疑可能酒後跌入幸無大礙。臉書《爆料公社》昨有網友貼跳河訊息，潘女事後po文「超痛又很冷」證明無恙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.buzzhand.net/uploads/df/f/889335/14479028286453.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.buzzhand.net%2Fuploads%2Fdf%2Ff%2F889335%2F14479028286453.jpg&h=10ce3545&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.buzzhand.net/uploads/df/f/889335/14479028304379.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.buzzhand.net%2Fuploads%2Fdf%2Ff%2F889335%2F14479028304379.jpg&h=ced20cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://bingfeng.tw/data/attachment/forum/201602/24/102554aclhzut2mgm2569z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbingfeng.tw%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201602%2F24%2F102554aclhzut2mgm2569z.jpg&h=184646da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b41f1352a575e724264d1bfa94559eaea6e86ed4","tid":188530,"uid":83648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T17:34:58.000Z"